              "name": "loreTitle",
              "fill": "#e8e6f0",
              "content": "Story",
              "fontFamily": "Rajdhani",
              "fontSize": 20,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "sMhZS",
              "name": "loreText",
              "fill": "#8b87a0",
              "content": "Growing up in Pallet Town, Red began his adventure by receiving his first Pokemon, Charmander, from Professor Oak. After repeatedly defeating his rival Blue, he collected eight badges and became the Pokemon League champion. However, victory did not satisfy him — he climbed to the icy peak of Mt. Silver to test his strength in solitude.",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
